query: 'SELECT User_Id, 
       First_Name, 
       Last_Name, 
       Email_Address, 
       Termination_Flag, 
       Department_Name, 
       NPN_Grouping, 
       Upline_Id,
       Upline_First_Name, 
       Upline_Last_Name, 
       Level_Seq, 
       MAX(Record_Load_date) AS Max_Record_Load_date
FROM [AIA_102].[AIA_AGENCY_EMP_HIER_DETAILS_HISTORY] AS emp
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [AIA_102].[AIA_AGENCY_PAYEE_DETAILS] AS payee
    WHERE payee.Employee_ID = emp.USER_ID
)
GROUP BY User_Id, 
         First_Name, 
         Last_Name, 
         Email_Address, 
         Termination_Flag, 
         Department_Name, 
         NPN_Grouping, 
         Upline_Id,
         Upline_First_Name, 
         Upline_Last_Name, 
         Level_Seq',
